Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:09.00,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3600)\bord1\3c&H1F1F1F&\be6\c&HFFFFFC&}so ra no wo to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:18.61,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:28.58,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:33.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:38.65,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:51.26,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, the happiness they sang about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:01:00.96,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:05.80,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:11.47,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:20.77,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:33.27,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:57.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like something that might wake the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:03:02.14,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}A Day in the Life - Rio Runs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:18.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:21.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:24.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At least it's edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:25.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a traditional food in my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:34.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is that {\i1}miso{\i0} thing? And it's made the same way as soy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:34.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:37.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some {\i1}miso{\i0} that my mother made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:42.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a lot more, so eat as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To Treize?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:49.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:53.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally received word from the Supply Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha and I will go to pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:03.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just about to run out of ammunition, medical supplies, and daily necessities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:07.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Carl's workshop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:11.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:17.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting a full workout on that bugle this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:20.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Heref youf hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:03.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your manners?\NWouldn't your dad cry if he saw you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:07.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh... Wike a' cabe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, for your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:23.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really can't stand them, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't blame those kids at the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:35.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who takes advantage of worthless superstitions to get some sort of profit is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:39.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones here taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H1C1B1D&\frz280.809\fs20\pos(216,124)}Very Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:46.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kanata has really gotten used to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always trying so hard, it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:06.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to admit she's diligent and full of enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:10.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not the type to think you can get by with just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you giving me that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:23.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Quit playing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H1C1B1D&\fs26\frx22\fry16\pos(220,115)\frz287.385}Atrocious
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It might take a while to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:45.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make any problems for Rio, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:09.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't expect you to be able to do this, but controlling the note with just the mouthpiece is one of the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:10.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:24.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How's life in the fort so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:26.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:30.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lax enough to say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:33.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost kind of jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:40.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're still on it, why'd you enlist in the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:43.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:47.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard I could learn how to play an instrument for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:54.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I also thought that it was important to protect my country!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:58.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind. Even if it's for money or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:04.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the ones with some ambition stay around longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:08.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm honored...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:13.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why did you join?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:21.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Well, probably the opposite of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:25.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They are pretty hard to find these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:29.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't hear brass instruments much outside the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:33.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard one a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just... like... yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:37.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:41.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound... of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:52.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:54.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:13.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:14.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:21.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, you'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:23.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mo-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:34.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:38.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:46.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat... snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:50.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Wait right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:10:00.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow. Snow. Snow. Where's the snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell would we have snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:11.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:22.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No. That's the last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:30.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine. Medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:33.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:35.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:40.11,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just about to run out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:44.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn the Supply Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I can't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:12.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:32.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:37.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:08.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:10.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:14.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the children didn't cause you any-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for my past disrespect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:22.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:36.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:38.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:50.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her fever is a bit high, but it should fall now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a serious disease at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:56.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's malaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:59.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Malaria? Only kids catch that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:04.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Adults can catch it under extreme fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:10.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When we take in new children,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,a lot of them catch it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:17.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The healthier they look, the higher the fever goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:21.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably been hiding it the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:25.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... will Kanata get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:26.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't stay like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:29.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:41.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:49.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:54.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is made with medicinal herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:58.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have her drink some a little later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:05.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:08.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:13.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To serve the people of this town is our joy and our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:16.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,May the blessings of all be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:25.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I- I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:29.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just like {\i1}miso{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:45.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:46.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miso{\i0} dregs are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:52.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When you make the soup, you strain the {\i1}miso{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:55.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The beans and things that are left - dregs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:17:00.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A leftover, or extra baggage. Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:07.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been like that since I was a kid. That's why... I decided to try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:10.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So that I wouldn't make problems for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:12.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:19.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lot more complex than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And selfish and spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:30.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I... say things?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:43.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:48.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That piece you were just humming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:51.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It went like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After hearing it just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:18.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:21.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to play that piece myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:30.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A sound that seems to echo from the heavens. That piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:35.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But {\i1}miso{\i0} dregs
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:37.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,are {\i1}miso{\i0} dregs no matter what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:39.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:44.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just leave ourselves indebted to some church.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:48.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This Takemikadzuchi is a treasure from another era.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:52.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are thousands of secrets just sleeping inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:57.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. If you want to know more, ask Noel later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:14.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:28.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:10.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably what the whole piece really sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:15.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All sorts of instruments, different parts ringing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They become a single music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like riding a tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:24.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A commander, a gunner, a driver,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:25.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and communications personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:30.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone works together to work a single tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is unneeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:36.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single note is unneeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:45.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that. Someone said it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.69,0:20:48.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The person I look up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and honor most.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:52.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As she told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:54.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:58.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think seniority and superiors exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:02.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So that those in lower ranks can make problems for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:06.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be able right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:09.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But just remember your frustration and powerlessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and the happiness of having someone to care for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:17.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, when you have to take care of someone, that will be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,your experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:24.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So make as many problems for me as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:26.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I made the same ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:30.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, when you do something wrong, you'll be scolded and punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:35.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you're suffering, if your heart might break, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:37.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:45.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:49.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I will make as many problems for you as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:51.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:58.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to go easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:06.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. I should have stayed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:10.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kanata, getting Rio to nurse her back to health...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:13.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it wasn't a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:17.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like it's just fatigue. She'll be fine if she sleeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.31,0:22:26.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemikadzuchi's lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:29.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I used it for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:31.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do it at a bad time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:35.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You listened to that piece, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:37.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:41.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And you said you wouldn't listen to it ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to hear it just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:47.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.61,0:22:51.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:58.00,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.36,0:23:01.47,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.65,0:23:19.23,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.41,0:23:25.32,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.41,0:23:34.10,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:38.70,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just take it easy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:40.33,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:44.67,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you tell me who you're asking to the dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.75,0:23:45.88,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:51.72,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.31,0:23:51.72,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}I know, you know, we'll be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:57.69,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.90,0:23:57.69,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}Can you count my precious hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:24:03.69,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All the usual words can't even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.95,0:24:09.53,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.85,0:24:14.48,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.98,0:24:26.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(320,180)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: The Rainy Sky - A Glass Rainbow
